{"tid":2015010,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"防彈經紀公司「對面60公尺」出現新冠肺炎確診者","createTime":"2020-05-13T11:17:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T12:05:12.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"744ab93cd43ec57ae66679d659782a3182e3e449","tid":2015010,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:17:14.000Z","msg":"南韓新冠肺炎（COVID-19）疫情在連假期間因爆發「梨泰院夜店集體感染」，好不容易趨緩的防疫成果倒退回一個月前，如今已有119人確診，也讓民眾生活再次陷入陰影中。13日卻傳出，一名確診者所在的公司大樓，就在防彈少年團（BTS）所屬的Big Hit娛樂正對面，直線距離只有60公尺。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4874/d4874801.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4874%2Fd4874801.jpg&h=d5b9d772&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲防彈少年團近日常在公司內直播，沒想到傳出正對面大樓有確診者。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／BANGTANTV）<br />\n<br />\n根據韓媒《news1》獨家報導，在首爾江南區三成洞的某辦公大樓中，其中一名公司的員工已確診新冠肺炎。因為擔心擴散，該大樓已經關閉，並將全面實施防疫工作。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4874/d4874787.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4874%2Fd4874787.jpg&h=59052760&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Big Hit娛樂正對面大樓出現新冠肺炎確診者，直線距離僅60公尺。（圖／翻攝自NEVER MAP）<br />\n<br />\n然而這棟大樓的正對面，就是Big Hit娛樂所在的MDM大樓。《ETtoday星光雲》記者根據南韓網友最常使用的「Naver地圖」，實際以網站提供的畫面比例尺測量，發現兩棟大樓的直線距離僅僅只有60公尺。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4874/d4874802.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4874%2Fd4874802.jpg&h=5b36d091&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Big Hit旗下男團TXT也經常在公司內直播。（圖／翻攝自VLIVE）<br />\n<br />\n由於防彈少年團和TXT等旗下藝人，近日直播畫面中經常顯示待在公司，也讓粉絲非常擔心。對此Big Hit娛樂回應，有接到相關單位通知：「當局將於13日同時對MDM實施防疫措施，Big Hit會誠實遵守當局的措施。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4845/d4845514.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4845%2Fd4845514.jpg&h=a4ec5df4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲防彈少年團近日常在公司內直播，沒想到傳出正對面大樓有確診者。（圖／翻攝自VLIVE）"},{"pid":"8c3d96fab164b1fa2287ca0b4d6320726e1f7f56","tid":2015010,"uid":165368,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:18:20.000Z","msg":"我冇事🤔"},{"pid":"209e56ea521f06f581ba86de6031b4b81a040732","tid":2015010,"uid":294121,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:19:19.000Z","msg":"淨係隊長中招就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09bfcff2334c19f06281a056243b04e058677f93","tid":2015010,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:26:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />差少少阿"},{"pid":"a82c91d0a8e8af8dd8778da6b2d3ff194044ef84","tid":2015010,"uid":198607,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:34:37.000Z","msg":"咩呀 征國唔係已經去咗梨泰院有事個間bar咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能佢先係隱形傳播者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec89bb39137ab1d5273d77e897e820887ef1e7ad","tid":2015010,"uid":211461,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T12:05:12.000Z","msg":"可惜團名唔係叫防菌少年團 準備RIP了"}]}